# {{ plugin_name }}

{{ description }}

A channel plugin for OpenComputer. Channels let the agent receive and
send messages on a third-party platform (Telegram, Discord, Slack, ...).

## Install

Copy this directory into one of:

- `~/.opencomputer/plugins/{{ plugin_id }}/` (global)
- `~/.opencomputer/profiles/<name>/plugins/{{ plugin_id }}/` (profile-local)

Or run `opencomputer plugin install <path-to-this-dir>`.

## Configure

Set whatever credentials the channel needs (bot tokens, etc.) as env
vars before starting `opencomputer gateway`. Document them here.

